I have been locked out of my account for several days now due to a log in issue i have spent many hours trying &#039;recommended&#039; ways to fix the issue and have written to player support, basically when i launch league of legends everything is fine then i type my password and try to login it authenticates my account details and starts to &#039;log on&#039; and from that point the client does nothing i have left the client for many hours assuming its just taking its time but it does not move from the logging on faze, i even reset my whole computer and re-downloaded league but the result was the same. 


it all started happening ever since the latest update (the release of mecha zero sion) so i can only assume its a problem with the league of legends client and it is out of my power to fix. 


if anybody has information on how to fix said issue please let me know thank you. (ONLY APPLIES TO PERSONAL HOTSPOT USERS)
